": "Onlar o kimselerdir ki mallar\u0131nda isteyen ve yoksun olanlar\u0131n haklar\u0131n\u0131 ay\u0131r\u0131rlar."}, {"id": 597661, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5400, "text": "Onlar o kimselerdir ki mallar\u0131nda isteyen ve yoksun olanlar\u0131n haklar\u0131n\u0131 ay\u0131r\u0131rlar."}, {"id": 597662, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5401, "text": "Onlar hesap g\u00fcn\u00fcn\u00fc tasdik ederler."}, {"id": 597663, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5402, "text": "Onlar Rab'lerinin cezas\u0131ndan korkarlar. [23,57; 51,19]"}, {"id": 597664, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5403, "text": "\u00c7\u00fcnk\u00fc Rab'lerinin azab\u0131ndan kimse emin olamaz."}, {"id": 597665, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5404, "text": "Onlar edep yerlerini, e\u015fleri ve cariyelerinden ba\u015fkas\u0131ndan korurlar. Yaln\u0131z bunlarla m\u00fcnasebeti olanlar ay\u0131planamazlar."}, {"id": 597666, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5405, "text": "Onlar edep yerlerini, e\u015fleri ve cariyelerinden ba\u015fkas\u0131ndan korurlar. Yaln\u0131z bunlarla m\u00fcnasebeti olanlar ay\u0131planamazlar."}, {"id": 597667, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5406, "text": "Ama bu s\u0131n\u0131r\u0131n \u00f6tesine ge\u00e7enler haddi a\u015fm\u0131\u015f, zul\u00fcm i\u015flemi\u015f olurlar."}, {"id": 597668, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5407, "text": "Onlar \u00fczerlerine ald\u0131klar\u0131 emanetlere ve verdikleri s\u00f6zlere riayet ederler."}, {"id": 597669, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5408, "text": "Onlar \u015fahitliklerini d\u00fcr\u00fcst\u00e7e ifa ederler."}, {"id": 597670, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5409, "text": "Onlar namazlar\u0131na tam dikkat ederler."}, {"id": 597671, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5410, "text": "\u0130\u015fte bunlar cennetlerde ikrama nail olacaklar."}, {"id": 597672, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5411, "text": "O k\u00e2firlere ne oluyor ki, seninle alay etmek maksad\u0131yla sa\u011fdan soldan da\u011f\u0131n\u0131k gruplar halinde, boyunlar\u0131n\u0131 uzatarak sana do\u011fru ko\u015fuyorlar."}, {"id": 597673, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5412, "text": "O k\u00e2firlere ne oluyor ki, seninle alay etmek maksad\u0131yla sa\u011fdan soldan da\u011f\u0131n\u0131k gruplar halinde, boyunlar\u0131n\u0131 uzatarak sana do\u011fru ko\u015fuyorlar."}, {"id": 597674, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5413, "text": "Onlardan her biri (iman etmeden) na\u00eem cennetine yerle\u015fmeye mi hevesleniyor?"}, {"id": 597675, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5414, "text": "(Hi\u00e7 heveslenmesin, hi\u00e7 kimsenin \u00f6teki insanlar \u00fczerinde b\u00f6b\u00fcrlenmeye hakk\u0131 olamaz). \u00c7\u00fcnk\u00fc Biz onlar\u0131 da, \u00f6b\u00fcr insanlar gibi, o bildikleri nesneden, meniden yaratt\u0131k. [77,20; 86,5-10]"}, {"id": 597676, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 570, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5415, "text": "Hay\u0131r, Allah'\u0131n nizam\u0131 onlar\u0131n sand\u0131\u011f\u0131 gibi de\u011fildir! Do\u011fular\u0131n ve bat\u0131lar\u0131n Rabbine yemin ederim ki, Biz onlar\u0131n yerine kendilerinden daha hay\u0131rl\u0131 insanlar getirmeye kadiriz. Bizim elimizden kurtulan, g\u00fcc\u00fcm\u00fcz\u00fcn yetmedi\u011fi hi\u00e7bir \u015fey yoktur. [40,57; 75,3-4; 56,60-61]"}, {"id": 597677, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 570, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5416, "text": "Hay\u0131r, Allah'\u0131n nizam\u0131 onlar\u0131n sand\u0131\u011f\u0131 gibi de\u011fildir! Do\u011fular\u0131n ve bat\u0131lar\u0131n Rabbine yemin ederim ki, Biz onlar\u0131n yerine kendilerinden daha hay\u0131rl\u0131 insanlar getirmeye kadiriz. Bizim elimizden kurtulan, g\u00fcc\u00fcm\u00fcz\u00fcn yetmedi\u011fi hi\u00e7bir \u015fey yoktur. [40,57; 75,3-4; 56,60-61]"}, {"id": 597678, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 570, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5417, "text": "Art\u0131k sen onlar\u0131 kendi hallerine b\u0131rak da, kendilerine v\u00e2d edilen g\u00fcn gelinceye kadar b\u00e2t\u0131la dals\u0131n, oynas\u0131nlar."}, {"id": 597679, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 570, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5418, "text": "O g\u00fcn onlar kabirlerinden \u00e7\u0131k\u0131p s\u00fcr'atle sanki bir hedefe varmak istercesine ko\u015farlar."}, {"id": 597680, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 570, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5419, "text": "G\u00f6zleri yerde, kendilerini ba\u015ftan a\u015fa\u011f\u0131 bir zillet kaplam\u0131\u015f durumdad\u0131r.\u0130\u015fte kendilerine v\u00e2d edilen g\u00fcn, bug\u00fcnd\u00fcr."}]